{"tid":2306870,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"戲院開埋呢幾日，咩人先會睇嗰套「白箱」唔睇鬼滅？抵佢畀中國封殺架喎","createTime":"2020-11-30T18:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T07:18:20.000Z","uid":198822,"like":15,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"daf1b2ed2015ee6550d4a7197f9b851348d9c251","tid":2306870,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"好似講有班女仔高中畢業之後，入哂動畫行業打滾，又聲優又cg師又劇本家，同其他人一齊由零整套動畫出嚟，唔覺有幾吸引，講埋動畫行業啲現實野咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個導演係好少有咁撐香港撐到畀大陸封埋套戲，咁但係都唔關套戲好唔好睇事，日本人又唔係老奉要支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真睇鬼滅喊完走人咪算，使咩咁深入知呢啲動畫點樣製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PDSyAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PDSyAh.jpg&h=61c39cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個女主角咁嘅樣，肉都唔露啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7db0bb520f0591d1ed428919876ea386d5ab1f6","tid":2306870,"uid":135445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"又反串"},{"pid":"bd03ee183849b09b7320e649055f88e5fd588062","tid":2306870,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df7d3287a568456257894df6cc04d34b9fda4881","tid":2306870,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4a94abb6c66c85393aa38415338f13e3a768686","tid":2306870,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae6200d097cc5fa2cfa1781e3ab04b67dbc29944","tid":2306870,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10363f8f67e695e60e39cb5bc55a79e5e1a1322e","tid":2306870,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"